                                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">Bahāʾī, Shaykh Bahāʾ al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn Ḥusayn ibn ʿAbd al-Ṣamad Ḥāris̱ī ʿĀmilī, 1546-1622</persName>
